<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />Hear my prayer, Yahweh, and listen to me;</para>

<para style="q1">listen to my weeping!</para>

<para style="q1">Do not be deaf to me,</para>

<para style="q1">for I am like a foreigner with you, a refugee like all my ancestors were.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Turn your gaze from me so that I may smile again</para>

<para style="q1">before I die."</para>
